Flicking seamlessly between English and French, Toulon captain Wilkinson insists: 'We're leading by a point with 40 minutes to play in a semi-final.

'F****** get it straight, OK. Set it in. Get it in your f****** heads what's happening.

'We f****** get in line and we go up - like Toulon do, OK?

'We're f****** here and there's 40 minutes to go. Change it - change it yourselves. We've got enough experience in here.'

